{
  "id": "adv_main_01_05_07",
  "title": "星見編1章28話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（数日の入院を勧められたが、そんな時間はない）\n（俺はなんとか頼み込んで退院してきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I am advised to remain in the hospital for a few days‚ but there is no time.）\n（I manage to convince them to discharge me.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.3333333333335,
          "startTime": 6.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2800,
          "startTime": 7.566666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "もういいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Should you be up already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二人だけなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it just the two of you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.67916100025177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい\nあ、でも練習はちゃんとやりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nOh‚ but don’t worry. All of us practiced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.458390061060587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが用意してくれた\nメニューに沿って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We used the schedule\nyou prepared‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.038185962041226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に{user}さんのパソコン\n見てしまったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ we checked your computer\nwithout permission.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.153974992800997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……実は話があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s something… we’d like to discuss with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.638941048353164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（やけに真顔だな。なんの話だろう）\n（思い当たるふしがない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Their expressions are oddly somber. I wonder what it could be.）\n（My mind draws a blank.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.034745930402735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まさかグランプリに出ないとか……\nいや、アイドルを辞めるとか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you going to drop out of the Grand Prix?\nOr‚ wait‚ are you going to quit as idols?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.76807926373606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.12177529212758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "デビューまでいろいろ指導してくれて\nありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for all your guidance\nfor our debut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.588441958794235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "誤解もあったけど{user}さんで\n良かったって、みんなで話してました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had our misunderstandings‚\nbut we all agree we’re lucky to have {user}-san as our manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.28844195879425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これからも{user}さんに\nマネジメントして欲しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why we’d like to ask {user}-san\nto continue managing us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.53109516975211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それが私達の偽らざる気持ちです\nでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s our honest and sincere desire.\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.997761836418746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "さくらと話したんです。このままじゃ\n{user}さんの体がもたないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and I talked about it‚\nand we think {user}-san is overworking yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.13109516975211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "私達がデビューしたらきっと\nもっともっと大変になるって…",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we have our debut‚\nI’m sure things will get even busier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.39102705197459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "自分達で頑張れればいいんですけど、きっとまだ\nそんな力はなくて、苦労かけてしまうだろうって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ideally‚ we’d be able to manage on our own‚\nbut we’re not that strong‚ so we’d end up relying on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.75769371864126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "…………それって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.66980055050976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.66980055050976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "どちらか\n一つのグループのマネジメントに専念して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want you\nto focus on managing one group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.40313388384308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "これ以上、二つのグループ兼任で\nマネジメントしたら、体がもちません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you continue managing both our groups\nit will take a toll on your health.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.51807719744174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "……だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6990104196164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（――どちらか片方だけ）\n（そんなこと、考えたこともなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Manage only one group.）\n（I never even considered that option.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.53234375294974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 105.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんにも話して許可はもらいました\n私もさくらも、メンバー全員、同じ考えでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We talked with Saegusa-san and got his permission.\nSakura and I and the rest of the members all feel the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.36567708628304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、俺なら大丈夫だ\n昨日倒れたのはたまたま……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on. I’ll be fine.\nI was just a little under the weather yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.03234375294977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてあげなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why not listen to them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.39901041961642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nグループ名、決まったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nWe decided on our group names.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.19901041961644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "さくらと話し合って……それで改めて分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and I talked… and we came to the realization",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.66567708628313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_07-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "どちらも{user}さんが作った\nグループだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "that {user}-san really are the one\nwho created both of our groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8008700527443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
